<lb ed="C I" n="0092a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>白實等造中興寺石像記</title></jhead></juan>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a01"/>夫妙性沖玄。至空凝絕。神功有跡於□□□□□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a02"/>慈□教。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">含</unclear>氣<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">戢</unclear>音。遺影自天。感祥□罕。<note n="0092001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30619;＝敷【史語所】</note><app n="0092001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">敷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30619;</rdg></app>慧日以<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">遍</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a03"/><note n="0092002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30620;＝照【史語所】</note><app n="0092002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">照</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30620;</rdg></app>。降法雨而<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">舒</unclear>霑。造意<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">聚</unclear>沙。登旡上之果。率心求掃。
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a04"/>當託不動之邦。　夫<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">識</unclear>超真觀。熟能與於此哉。
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a05"/>惟大魏鎮遠將軍步兵校尉前河北太守鎮固城大
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a06"/>都督周城縣開國男。白　公名實。字雙城。<note n="0092003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00362;＝體【史語所】</note><app n="0092003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">體</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00362;</rdg></app>道群英。
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a07"/>志超遠略。業因曠善。德美今<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">時</unclear>。才實文武。器過瑚璉。
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a08"/>名播六郡。振嚮三秦。自<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">參</unclear>朝政。躍馬邊戎。值四方多
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a09"/>事。蠢徒<note n="0092004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB15137;＝競【史語所】</note><app n="0092004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">競</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB15137;</rdg></app>紛。時委專征。剋平多難。逞不世之奇功。懷
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a10"/>謀略於匈衿。楚敵知人。齊稱盼乎。<note n="0092005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00502;＝驅【史語所】</note><app n="0092005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">驅</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00502;</rdg></app><note n="0092006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04572;＝策【史語所】</note><app n="0092006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">策</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04572;</rdg></app>盡功。住無不
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a11"/>彌。依仁踐義。<note n="0092007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30562;＝權【史語所】</note><app n="0092007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">權</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30562;</rdg></app>而□勇。洪勳臣積。又彰朝野。流歌詠
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a12"/>於時口。傳芳<note n="0092008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30621;＝聲【史語所】</note><app n="0092008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">聲</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30621;</rdg></app>於史籍。帶五縣之名邑。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">佩</unclear>三陽之一
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a13"/>居。乃<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">成</unclear>物沃壤。<note n="0092009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30476;＝寇【史語所】</note><app n="0092009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">寇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30476;</rdg></app>敵催鋒。竊盜歛跡。煎無遺孑。<note n="0092010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30622;＝隸【史語所】</note><app n="0092010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">隸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30622;</rdg></app>屬
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a14"/>慶其威德。左夏伏其才武。遠近慕義。志念道場。心<note n="0092011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB06270;＝移【史語所】</note><app n="0092011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">移</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB06270;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a15"/>彼<note n="0092012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30623;＝岸【史語所】</note><app n="0092012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">岸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30623;</rdg></app>。嗟雙林之已逝。演三會之難邀。　大統三年歲
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a16"/>次戊午四月己丑朔八日丙申。率固城上下村邑。諸
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a17"/>郡守。大都督。戌主。十州武義等。共崇斯福。為國主大
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a18"/>王　□史造中興寺石像。地皆嚴淨。幽明<app source="0092002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">照</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30620;</rdg></app>曜。此之
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a19"/>淨土。立功累年。營構方就。梵宮凝麗。其如自然。房廊
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a20"/>周廓。<note n="0092013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB17893;＝跨【史語所】</note><app n="0092013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">跨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB17893;</rdg></app>躡相<note n="0092014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30624;＝尋【史語所】</note><app n="0092014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">尋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30624;</rdg></app>。畫妙飾疑神造。菩提一念。漸蹬無<note n="0092015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30625;＝極【史語所】</note><app n="0092015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">極</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30625;</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a21"/>凡有感類。莫不<note n="0092016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30614;＝嘉【史語所】</note><app n="0092016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">嘉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30614;</rdg></app>尚。殖因既著。業果來臻。勒石刊碑。
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a22"/>傳之弗朽。　其辭曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a23"/>法輪悠邈。體道遐宣。世惟獨住。<note n="0092017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30626;＝虛【史語所】</note><app n="0092017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30626;</rdg></app>沖自天。積塵無礙
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a24"/>聚<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">不</unclear>有細。兜率難<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">樂</unclear>。王宮易遷。返迷尋夜。救溺苦邊。
<lb ed="C I" n="0092a25"/>□□□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">遊</unclear>。幽途可涉。夫君寤<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">道</unclear>。．．．
